    public final class OnSubscribeToMultimap<T,K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable.OnSubscribe<java.util.Map<K,java.util.Collection<V>>>, Func0<java.util.Map<K,java.util.Collection<V>>>
    Maps the elements of the source observable into a multimap (Map<K, Collection<V>>) where each key entry has a collection of the source's values.
